metadata.name: Meta-Artisan Original Cabin Luggage #1
metadata.description:
The unmistakable RIMOWA Original aluminum suitcase with its distinctive grooves is regarded as one of the most iconic luggage designs of all time.

Features the RTFKT Special Limited Edition “Wandersmith” Anti-FUD pattern print, made for next-gen world builders and explorers. Forgeable to redeem your physical luggage during the Forging event [ date TBC ].
